  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate slum child in Kenya</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Non formal schools in the slums of Nairobi face formidable challenges with lack of teaching staff and learning materials. We are working with 8 non-formal schools in Ruaraka, Nairobi which suffer from a severe shortage of teachers (with a teacher to student ratio of 1:40) and also a shortage of reading materials. With your donation, our team of 15 volunteers are teaching and carrying out targeted mentorship for the children in these schools.</narrative>
  </description>
